data.description: Back on the market, now's your chance! NEW HVAC 2024, NEW ROOF, plumbing, and electrical updates before closing!   Are you Downsizing or a First Time Buyer - this is a great home to make your own! Walk in the front door to the 3-bedroom split floor plan. You’ll notice the living room/dining room combo and tile floors throughout. Enjoy the spacious backyard nestled on .25 acres, completely fenced and private. The tree line at the back border provides tons of shade and no backyard neighbors. So much extra outdoor space for entertaining and for storing all the toys. Great location close to shopping at the newly renovated Publix supermarket at Pearl Brittan Plaza and just a few miles to downtown Ocala.
